For example, nobody believes

00:38:32.840 --> 00:38:34.060
♪ Hanging in the sky ♪

00:38:35.120 --> 00:38:35.160
♪ Let me wander with you ♪

00:38:35.160 --> 00:38:37.360
there would be blooms on this dead tree.

