♪ Who dares to break this chaos? ♪

00:38:47.800 --> 00:38:51.260
♪ Who can shatter fate’s wall? ♪

00:38:51.770 --> 00:38:55.210
♪ Who else dares to fight alone like me? ♪

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:58.530
♪ Who dares to defy all odds? ♪

