Why don't we

00:39:06.450 --> 00:39:07.040
♪ Who can relight
the streets’ lost fire? ♪

00:39:07.040 --> 00:39:08.370
work a miracle together

00:39:08.930 --> 00:39:10.450
by instilling beliefs in everyone?

